lementor-column elementor-field-group-field_81071c9 elementor-col-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<label for=\"form-field-field_81071c9\" class=\"elementor-field-label\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tOrganisation name (if applicable):\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/label>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<input size=\"1\" type=\"text\" name=\"form_fields[field_81071c9]\" id=\"form-field-field_81071c9\" class=\"elementor-field elementor-size-lg  elementor-field-textual\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-field-type-textarea elementor-field-group elementor-column elementor-field-group-field_77f8c45 elementor-col-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<label for=\"form-field-field_77f8c45\" class=\"elementor-field-label\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tYou can adjust, change, or delete any part of it as needed\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/label>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<textarea class=\"elementor-field-textual elementor-field  elementor-size-lg\" name=\"form_fields[field_77f8c45]\" id=\"form-field-field_77f8c45\" rows=\"15\">Dear Shabana Mahmood and Amy Rees,\r\n\r\nI am extremely concerned by the horrifying accounts of pregnant women in prison being cuffed during childbirth and antenatal examinations.\r\n\r\nI am writing to urge you to commission the Prison and Probation Ombudsman (PPO) to conduct an independent investigation into the widespread use of unlawful restraints on pregnant women by Sodexo Staff at HMP Bronzefield.\r\n\r\nThe use of unlawful restraints on pregnant women over a period of years raises the Secretary of State's obligations under Articles 3 and 8 of the European Convention of Human Rights (right to freedom from torture, inhuman or degrading treatment and right to a private or family life).\r\n\r\nThis harrowing ill-treatment of women must be investigated without delay to ensure it can never happen again.\r\n\r\nKind regards,<\/textarea>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-field-type-recaptcha_v3 elementor-field-group elementor-column elementor-field-group-field_b4